raw_text = "~ start
## 5pm
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: Hey Mabes, how'd the presentation go??
Mabel: BABE
Mabel: I survived 🥲
Mabel: I was picked first and ugh
Mabel: ALL eyes were on me and it was so nervewrecking!!
Mabel: Thought: My class is all boys and they were just staring at me...
Mabel: img: mabel/191
Mabel: Barely, but I did it
Player: 🥳 Awesome
Mabel: I hope I didn't look like a train wreck
Player: You still pulled it off!
Mabel: 🥹 I did didn't I?
Mabel: Thanks babe
Mabel: What would I do without my adorable boyfriend 🥰
Mabel: It's DONE and I never have to think about it again!! Hooray!
Player: 🥳
Mabel: Hehe
Mabel: Ooh speaking of stuff to do 😅
Mabel: That Sorority thing is this Friday right?
Mabel: Are you gonna be able to come? 🥺
Mabel: I'd feel a million times less nervous if you were there with me
Mabel: Thought: Something tells me there's gonna be a lot of boys
Player: I don't think I can make it babe
Player: The invite went to someone else 🥲
Mabel: Oh..
do echo_set([\"192\"])
Mabel: Thought: Totally fine right?
Mabel: Thought: Don't tear up now Mabes...
Mabel: Thought: It'll be totally okay!
Mabel: Oh okay! 😊
Player: They only had only one spot
Mabel: Ugh that sucks
Player: Sorry..
Mabel: Noo it's okay, I totally get it! 🥰
Mabel: Thought: I really wanted you there but..
Mabel: Thought: It's fine. I'm a big girl, I can do one party on my own...
Mabel: I'll just have to be a brave Agent for the night hehe!
Player: Yeah. Have fun, okay?
Player: I'll try to be in the next one!
do echo_clear()
Mabel: I'll try my best! And okay! I'll hold you to it 😚
Mabel: Okay I need to sleep before I fully zombify
Mabel: You don't want me turning into one 😘
Mabel: So gn babe hehe
Player: Night Mabes
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
